    <li>You have home insurance with another insurer and you know your renewal month</li>
    <li>You're over 18 years of age</li>
    <li>You own and live at the property. Excludes any properties you rent out</li>
    <li>You haven't already told us your home insurance renewal date</li>
  </ul>
